transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Thyacra, this is Olivia speaking, who do I have the pleasure of speaking with today?

Speaker 2: Yes, my name is Travis Lino.

Speaker 1: Hi, Travis, how are you?

Speaker 2: I'm doing wonderful.

Speaker 1: I placed an order with you guys and I got the tracking number stuff and it never showed up.

Speaker 2: It said it came, let me see, I'll tell you the date.

Speaker 1: I don't know why it's not coming up right now.

Speaker 2: Oh, here it is.

Speaker 1: I have the tracking number.

Speaker 2: No, that's okay.

Speaker 1: Can you just confirm your date of birth?

Speaker 2: I should have everything.

Speaker 1: Yeah, 8-28-1968.

Speaker 2: Yeah, okay, and you're located at 39811 North 3rd Street, Phoenix, Arizona, 85086?

Speaker 1: Yes, ma'am.

Speaker 2: Okay, and so it shows delivered, but you're saying you didn't receive it?

Speaker 1: No, no, I never got anything.

Speaker 2: We have mailboxes, like community mailboxes, that are locked and there's no way to get in there.

Speaker 1: Yeah, okay, so yeah, it does show USPS with that tracking number that it was delivered January 24th at 10:17 a.m. to the 39811 North 3rd Street, Phoenix, Arizona address?

Speaker 2: Yes, ma'am.

Speaker 1: Okay, you're saying the boxes, that your mailboxes are locked, but would the package have been left in the mailbox or at your front door potentially?

Speaker 2: I don't know how they do it, but we get deliveries here a lot to our house, and there was nothing delivered to the front door for me.

Speaker 1: Yeah, okay.

Speaker 2: Did it say it was a mailbox or a front door?

Speaker 1: It just says it was sent to the 39811 North 3rd Street address.

Speaker 2: You know, we're not USPS, we're just a company that ships through them.

Speaker 1: Okay, so I can send you out a one-time replacement, and I can do signature upon delivery.

Speaker 2: That'd be perfect.

Speaker 1: Okay, we can just, well, I'm sure it won't be a problem if we do signature upon delivery,

Speaker 2: but I do have to mention per protocol that we can only do this once, which is totally fine.

Speaker 1: Okay, so great.

Speaker 2: This is going to be 25 pills, Viagra HEV, 100 milligrams, shipping to 39811 North 3rd Street,

Speaker 1: Phoenix, Arizona.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Yeah, so these will be out to you probably by next week.

Speaker 2: I would think next Friday at the latest, probably Tuesday through Thursday.

Speaker 1: Awesome.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Thank you very much.

Speaker 1: I appreciate it.

Speaker 2: Thanks, Travis.

Speaker 1: All right, you have a great day.

Speaker 2: Yeah, bye.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
